data.description: A grand front porch adds timeless curb appeal and takes you back in time to simpler days when friends & family gathered together for tea & conversation. The allure of living on The Avenue still has that same special feel it had in 1900 when this stunning home was built. The simple yet impressive design of this home offers much of the original charm from over 100 years ago including the original floors, moldings and staircase. The main floor offers large rooms including a living room with beautiful fireplace, dining room, kitchen,  bath and main floor laundry.  Up the spectacular, original staircase, you are greeted by the upper level landing, true to the homes tradition. Here you will find 3 bedrooms & 1 full bath.  The unfinished attic provides unlimited potential as the basement provides unlimited storage.  The detached garage is massive & includes one stall set up as a workshop.  This beauty won't last long!
